.Dd July 8, 2010
.Dt LT 1
.Os
.Sh NAME
.Nm lt
.Nd show a tree-like output of any directory
.Sh SYNOPSIS
.Nm
.Op Ar directory ...
.Sh DESCRIPTION
The
.Nm
script shows a tree of the path specified by
.Ar directory ,
including files and subdirectories, much like the
.Nm tree
utility.
If no directory is specified, the current directory
is shown.
.Sh SEE ALSO
.Xr find 1
